milestones.description: Shaiman Anwar has broken the record for most sixes (16) in ODIs for UAE, going past Rameez Shahzad's 15
This is the lowest match aggregate (355) involving teams U.A.E. & Afghanistan in ODIs
Gulbadin Naib has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Dawlat Zadran's 5
Shahzad has scored 14 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Rahmat Shah's record

stories.title: Rashid not giving up on World-Cup slot yet
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v UAE, World Cup Qualifier 2018, Super Sixes, Harare
stories.seoTitle: Rashid Khan not giving up on World-Cup slot yet
stories.summary: Afghanistan's path through the Super Sixes to the 2019 World Cup is a complicated one, but the legspinner wants his team to concentrate on winning their last match and then "see what happens"

stories.title: Rashid Khan's five-for keeps Afghanistan alive

stories.seoTitle: Rashid Khan's five-for keeps Afghanistan alive
stories.summary: Afghanistan slipped to 54 for 5 in the chase, but eventually overcame a plucky United Arab Emirates, who lost their appetite for a fight on a stiflingly hot afternoon
